If you are looking for good  Nasi Lemak , Mee Rebus or Lotong .. this is the best stall in this area.  The Nasi is Lemak fragnant and light which went well the  healthy Lotong .   Price wise is super reasonable and a good portion .

Heavily recommended and I will visit it whenever I am around the estate.
